description: Try our easy to follow Beef & Sprout Stir-fry recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Stir-fry,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Rice,Egg free,Low sugar,Beef,Dairy free
name: Beef & Sprout Stir-fry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Cook rice according to instructions on packet.
Meanwhile, heat a wok or frying pan until hot then add oil.
Add beef and stir fry until lightly browned. Add onion, celery, crunchy combo and capsicum; stir-fry vigorously for 2 minutes.
Add honey, soy sauce and water if required (water will only be needed if the sauce is not liquid enough), add snow pea sprouts and bean sprouts stir through to combine sauce evenly.
Serve on a bed of rice Asian style.
